---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="AI-Powered Life Sciences Platform">
  <h1>AI-Powered Life Sciences Platform</h1>

  <p style="font-size: 22px; margin-top: 16px;">
    Shaping a complex platform experience that helped scientific teams work more
    efficiently with intelligent tools and structured workflows.
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--divider);"></div>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Context</h2>
    <p>
      Scientific and research teams often worked across fragmented systems, manual
      workflows, and highly specialized tools that created friction in daily work.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Challenge</h2>
    <p>
      How might we create a more unified, intuitive platform experience that supports
      complex scientific tasks without adding operational overhead?
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Approach</h2>
    <p>
      Applied product thinking, workflow analysis, and platform design principles to
      clarify user needs, structure information, and improve task efficiency.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Outcome</h2>
    <p>
      Helped shape a more coherent platform direction that supported usability,
      scale, and better alignment between user workflows and product architecture.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>